    <!-- Visualization & Content Choices: 1. **Comparison of Methods**: Report Info: Four distinct methods with varying potential. Goal: Compare. Viz: Horizontal Bar Chart (Chart.js) comparing 'Potential Hourly Rate' & 'Accessibility'. Interaction: Hover for tooltips. Justification: Provides a quick, data-driven visual guide for users to decide where to focus. 2. **Method Details**: Report Info: Descriptions and steps for each method. Goal: Organize/Inform. Presentation: Interactive cards to select a method, with details displayed in a dedicated content area. Tutorials are in collapsible accordions. Interaction: Click to select method, click to expand/collapse tutorial steps. Justification: Prevents information overload and allows focused learning. 3. **Key Stats**: Report Info: Potential earnings (‚Ç¨50-‚Ç¨200/month). Goal: Inform. Presentation: Styled 'stat cards' with large text. Justification: Highlights motivating figures. Library/Method: All implemented with Chart.js, HTML/CSS/JS. -->
